42:46.000 --> 42:47.010
- Good for you.

42:49.090 --> 42:50.754
Now what?

42:50.754 --> 42:52.940
- Okay, okay, okay.

42:52.940 --> 42:53.773
I have a gun.

42:54.630 --> 42:56.567
It's in my car, come on.

42:56.567 --> 42:58.113
