43:05.810 --> 43:06.710
Yes, yes?

43:06.710 --> 43:09.183
Okay, okay, good, good, good.

43:17.370 --> 43:19.790
Lock the door, listen for me.

43:19.790 --> 43:23.323
I'll be right back, I promise.

43:23.323 --> 43:24.156
Okay.

43:26.094 --> 43:28.177
(grunts)

43:30.045 --> 43:32.962
(foreboding music)

43:41.995 --> 43:44.328
