47:10.256 --> 47:12.006
- [Lestor] All right.

47:19.980 --> 47:22.473
- Now it's as if we--
- Guys, bro?

47:22.473 --> 47:24.050
- I told you we should've
killed that black girl

47:24.050 --> 47:24.933
