47:32.610 --> 47:34.310
We've got bigger fish to fry.

47:34.310 --> 47:35.550
I want you to get the driver

47:35.550 --> 47:37.460
into the truck with the explosives,

47:37.460 --> 47:39.410
and I want this rig ready
to go within the hour,

47:39.410 --> 47:41.040
am I understood?

47:41.040 --> 47:42.640
Now where the fuck fuck is my--

47:42.640 --> 47:44.360
- Don't move!

47:44.360 --> 47:46.030
Drop your weapons on the floor.

47:46.030 --> 47:48.053
Do it now, or I'll shoot.

47:57.730 --> 47:59.730
Now kick your weapons towards the walls.

48:01.660 --> 48:02.995
- Now what?

48:02.995 --> 48:04.130
You gonna shoot all of us?

48:04.130 --> 48:06.530
- I'm gonna shoot you if
you don't shut the fuck up.

48:06.530 --> 48:08.680
- Do it, you can't stop what's coming.

48:08.680 --> 48:10.076
- Don't make me.
- Hm?

48:10.076 --> 48:15.076
(gun fires)
(Max grunts in pain)

48:20.185 --> 48:21.665
- Fuck.

48:21.665 --> 48:23.020
- [Max] That bitch
almost shot my foot off!

48:23.020 --> 48:26.214
- Yo man, she locked herself
in the van, you idiot!

48:26.214 --> 48:27.650
- Fuck the van, what about my foot?

48:27.650 --> 48:29.237
- All right, both of you shut up a second.

48:29.237 --> 48:31.486
