50:44.750 --> 50:48.060
- If I go, we all go, you
dumb white motherfucker.

50:48.060 --> 50:49.570
- [Nova] Leave her alone.

50:49.570 --> 50:51.033
She's a nice person.

50:53.390 --> 50:54.223
- Nova?

50:56.186 --> 50:58.270
(somber music)

50:58.270 --> 50:59.103
Is that you?

51:00.805 --> 51:03.674
- Why did you come back?

51:03.674 --> 51:05.257
You didn't have to.

51:07.074 --> 51:08.907
Why did you come back?

51:11.513 --> 51:13.200
- I can't explain it.

51:13.200 --> 51:14.313
- You saved me.

51:16.764 --> 51:18.133
I didn't wanna drug you.

51:20.150 --> 51:23.743
But I had to, or they
would've killed you on sight.

51:24.830 --> 51:25.863
- Then help me.

51:26.770 --> 51:27.603
Do something.

51:29.290 --> 51:30.123
- No.

51:31.390 --> 51:32.713
She ain't gonna do shit.

51:37.780 --> 51:38.973
