51:46.350 --> 51:47.483
- Nova.

51:50.330 --> 51:54.893
Just tell them to back away
from the van, and I'll come out.

51:57.340 --> 51:58.173
- Why?

51:59.210 --> 52:00.560
What are you gonna do then?

52:04.670 --> 52:06.170
- I'll give you what you want.

52:07.900 --> 52:10.410
Just give me the van driver and I'll leave

52:10.410 --> 52:12.053
