make it till morning anyway.

52:26.660 --> 52:27.610
- We've got a deal.

52:28.700 --> 52:33.173
Back away from the van, and I'll come out.

52:36.684 --> 52:39.033
- Back up.

52:39.033 --> 52:42.783
