53:33.673 --> 53:35.423
You're a good person.

53:36.630 --> 53:39.250
You may have gotten into
it with the wrong people,

53:40.572 --> 53:42.655
but you're not like them.

53:44.013 --> 53:44.846
No.

53:46.836 --> 53:47.836
Put it down.

53:49.625 --> 53:51.093
Yeah.

53:51.093 --> 53:51.926
Okay.

53:53.493 --> 53:54.326
- Nova.

53:57.163 --> 53:59.397
What are you doing?

53:59.397 --> 54:01.853
You know you can't trust them.

54:03.240 --> 54:05.270
- Nova, don't listen to him.

54:05.270 --> 54:07.553
- You remember what you told me?

54:07.553 --> 54:10.847
What they did to you when
you were a little girl?

54:12.767 --> 54:13.743
How they hurt you?

54:15.490 --> 54:18.652
Never gonna let that
happen again, are you?

54:18.652 --> 54:19.652
Never again.

54:34.732 --> 54:38.065
(emergency sirens wail)

54:39.542 --> 54:40.375
(Fay grunts)

54:40.375 --> 54:41.964
- Okay, synced up.

54:41.964 --> 54:43.164
- Put that in the truck.

54:44.190 --> 54:46.160
Wrap this shit show up, people.

54:46.160 --> 54:47.450
Wheels up in five minutes.

54:47.450 --> 54:49.780
Dallas, gas up the truck,
I want it topped off.

54:49.780 --> 54:50.680
- [Dallas] Got it.

54:51.840 --> 54:53.602
- Yeah, we're good.

54:53.602 --> 54:56.869
(timer beeps)

54:56.869 --> 54:57.702
