56:43.392 --> 56:45.720
- Nah, I heard the noise, man.

56:45.720 --> 56:47.293
Needed to get out of the street.

56:47.293 --> 56:48.583
It's crazy out there.

56:50.250 --> 56:51.885
- Yeah.

56:51.885 --> 56:53.285
About to get crazy here too.

56:55.690 --> 56:58.650
Say I find myself in need of
another able-bodied individual.

56:58.650 --> 57:00.850
